1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:06,000
Las alertas de inundación dependen de lo que se cae primero
en una emergencia: la conectividad.

2
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:12,000
Flood warnings depend on what fails first:
the network itself.

3
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:21,000
En el Litoral argentino, cuando se cae la red,
alguien tiene que seguir mirando el río.

4
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:30,000
We are building Acuífero + Vigía:
offline-first flood warnings, with Gemma close to the evidence.

5
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:38,000
Vigía es la capa humana.
Un voluntario envía un reporte local en castellano rioplatense.

6
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:46,000
"Che, el agua ya pasó la marca y viene con barro.
Hay familias en la zona baja."

7
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:55,000
Gemma lo convierte en evidencia estructurada:
peligro, urgencia, señales y acción recomendada.

8
00:00:55,000 --> 00:01:05,000
Acuífero is the fixed node.
It watches camera evidence near critical sites.

9
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:17,000
The node builds a temporal evidence pack from curated frames
and asks Gemma for a node assessment.

10
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:30,000
Output: assessment level, temporal summary,
reasoning summary, critical evidence.

11
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:38,000
Now the network is gone.
Volunteer reports queue locally.

12
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:48,000
The fixed node keeps reasoning.
The local alert still fires, with an audible siren.

13
00:01:48,000 --> 00:02:00,000
Connectivity returns. The queue drains.
No data loss. No silent failure.

14
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:12,000
A red badge is not enough.
Every alert carries reasoning, rule trace and evidence.

15
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:25,000
Operators see why the alert fired
and what evidence to review first.

16
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:36,000
The exported alert package is schema-tagged for SINAGIR,
Argentina's national disaster-risk system.

17
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:48,000
Aligned with the Plan Nacional 2025–2029
priorities on local preparedness.

18
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:56,000
Today: an MVP demo on public and simulated scenarios.

19
00:02:56,000 --> 00:03:00,000
Acuífero + Vigía. Local flood intelligence.
